In the Matter of LOUIS K. LIGGETT COMPANY, Bankrupt. In re GIBBONS REALTY COMPANY, Appellant. No. 240. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 15, 1935. Yankauer, Davidson & Mann, of New York City ,(C. Ira Funston, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Milbank, Tweed, Hope & Webb, of New York City (H. Struve Hensel and Erwin H. Steif, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
